The paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to improve recognition accuracy, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The dataset is collected from the internet, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) category. Finally, the paper discusses the vulnerability of face recognition systems to attacks, which falls under the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) category.
